<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">أَنْشَدَنَا أَبُو بَكْرٍ الصُّولِيُّ لِنَفْسِهِ:</span> <span class="c1">"<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[البحر المجتث]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>أَطَلْتَ بِالْهَجْرِ سُقْمِي ... لَمَّا جَعَلْتُكَ هَمِّي<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>أَسَأْتَ فِي كُلِّ قَوْلٍ ... وَجُرْتَ فِي كُلِّ حُكْمٍ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>⦗١٥١⦘<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>إِنْ كَانَ حُبُّكَ جُرْمِي ... فَقَدْ وَقَعَتُ بِجُرْمِي<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>أَمَا تَرَى فِعْلَ لَحْظِي ... فِيمَا جَنَاهُ بِرَغْمِي<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>رَأَى بِطَرْفِكَ سَقَمًا ...<span class="c5"> فَقَالَ:</span> هَبْهُ لِجِسْمِي<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>فَصِرْتُ شَبَهَكَ يَحْكِي ... سِقَامَ عَيْنَيْكَ سُقْمِي"<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>